{"tid":2005294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普否決國會限制總統對伊朗宣戰權力議案","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T05:06:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a38e408ee79a47041044e5afee8271278c291ad5","tid":2005294,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:23:44.000Z","msg":"2020-05-07 11:41:15<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國會兩院先前雙雙通過決議，限制總統對伊朗宣戰的權力，但美國總統川普於當地時間6日對這項決議動用否決權，指稱此項決議是美國民主黨人為了分裂共和黨、贏得年底的大選而使出的策略。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，川普在白宮發布的聲明中表示，這項「極具侮辱性」的決議是由民主黨人發起，是為了分裂共和黨、贏得今年11月3日的總統大選所使出的策略，少數投下贊成票的共和黨人正中他們下懷。<br />\n<br />\n雖然川普所屬的共和黨在參議院擁有53席對47席的多數優勢，但由於少數共和黨人跑票，參議院在今年2月以55對45的票數通過上述決議，民主黨人佔多數的眾議院也在3月以227對186票通過。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院預計最快會在當地時間7日表決是否推翻總統的否決權。儘管少數共和黨人先前曾跑票而讓決議順利通過，但這次兩院很可能無法投出三分之二多數以推翻總統的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3157609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157609&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=d614642e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3157609&h=d832d68c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3157609</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-congress/trump-vetoes-iran-war-powers-resolution-idUSKBN22I36O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-mideast-crisis-congress%2Ftrump-vetoes-iran-war-powers-resolution-idUSKBN22I36O&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=1bb8551c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-mideast-crisis-congress%2Ftrump-vetoes-iran-war-powers-resolution-idUSKBN22I36O&h=fd252cb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-congress/trump-vetoes-iran-war-powers-resolution-idUSKBN22I36O</a>"},{"pid":"d482591c4d3ee5d7b0cbf7da1e8e50c44f140bce","tid":2005294,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d06ece3d75ab5db1e3dc88f89776a1317af809","tid":2005294,"uid":64743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲削自己權議案都晒氣"},{"pid":"79032d9300243401b84ec3c2a13f90674d8eca3d","tid":2005294,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />癡鳩線"},{"pid":"a9c676453b4adf4a2dbd6a95d0d2d552f684356e","tid":2005294,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"支那暫時太強唔可以打，可以打伊朗出下氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bf92f609388c27c8feaa4a0e0a59c7b3939c1a","tid":2005294,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"打伊朗托柒咩<br />\n叫以色列食自己啦"},{"pid":"1787a9066cf2147b73863371ca1a65585f2d1f6c","tid":2005294,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93bf92f609388c27c8feaa4a0e0a59c7b3939c1a","tid":2005294,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"打伊朗托柒咩<br />\n叫以色列食自己啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"伊朗係支那盟友，盟友最好梗係自身難保啦"}]}